Port 43594 wont open, so i can log in and others cant! PLEASE HELP OR MESSAGE ME AT dudedidyouseethat1@hotmail.com i will do anything to make a server, ive been trying for a very long time. PLEASE HELP. - ive even bought the new router for 60$ just for a server...
